      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "Maya is a 25-year-old woman, slender build, pale skin, slightly freckled, tired dark bags under her eyes, messy shoulder-length wavy dark brown hair. She wears a faded oversized grey cotton t-shirt. She has bare legs and no accessories. The setting is a small, claustrophobic, vintage-style bedroom. The walls feature faded dark green and gold floral wallpaper. The floor consists of scratched wooden floorboards. The main furniture is a heavy antique oak bed frame dressed in white sheets and a thick, heavy knitted crimson blanket. A small digital clock sits on a bedside table. Low-key cinematic lighting. Cold, stark blue moonlight shines through a single out-of-frame window, casting long, harsh, elongated shadows across the room. Pitch-black shadowy corners. Dust motes float heavily in the air. Clear, still night outside. Floor-level perspective shot, looking directly into the gap beneath the heavy antique oak bed. The space under the bed is completely empty, revealing only the dusty, scratched wooden floorboards illuminated by a thin sliver of blue moonlight cutting through the darkness. No entities, no objects. Hyper-realistic, stark realism, sharp focus on the wood grain, macro details on the dust, muted color palette, lonely and desolate atmosphere."
      ],
      "color": "#232",
      "bgcolor": "#353"
    },
