      "widgets_values": [
        "Slow dolly crawl backward. The environment remains entirely still. The thin sliver of moonlight shifts infinitesimally across the floorboards. Thick dust motes drift lazily through the shaft of light. No sudden movements, purely environmental realism.\n\nSound Design Prompt\nThe loud heartbeat abruptly stops, leaving a vacuum of sound. A long, shaky, and deeply relieved sigh from Maya echoes from above the camera. The faint, distant whistling of wind outside the window."
